# Design Systems Convention

## Struktura preset

```
design-systems/<preset-name>/
├── DESIGN.md                      # Main spec (palette + typography + voice + layout)
├── tokens.example.json            # Working example dla referencji
├── inspiration.md                 # Industry references + URL screenshots
└── samples/
    ├── hero.html                  # HTML snippet
    ├── features.html
    ├── cta.html
    ├── pricing.html
    └── full-page.html             # Combined sample dla preview
```

## 7 presets do zaimplementowania

| # | Name | Tagline | Vibe |
|---|------|---------|------|
| 1 | `default` | Bezpieczny start dla każdego projektu | Neutral, Inter, zinc grays, blue accent |
| 2 | `monolith-meadow` | Solidność z natury (heritage/hospitality/wellness) | Earthy, Recoleta, sage/terracotta, cream surfaces |
| 3 | `tech-modern` | Crisp, fast, opinionated (dev tools) | Geist, indigo gradient, sharp shadows |
| 4 | `warm-editorial` | Słowa mają wagę (magazyny/blogs/journalism) | Tiempos, cream, brick red, 65ch reading width |
| 5 | `brutalist` | Statement piece (stand out brands) | Söhne Breit, B/W + pure RGB accents, radius 0, 4px borders |
| 6 | `soft-pastel` | Approachable, calm (wellness/edu/lifestyle) | Recoleta soft, dusty pastels, rounded |
| 7 | `dark-cinematic` | Premium (SaaS/dev tools/finance) | Inter Display, jet black, neon accents, backdrop blur |

Pełne specs (palettes / typography / voice / layout / inspiration) w `.docs/DESIGN_SYSTEMS.md`.

